{"name": "barbara-updater", "metadata": {"name": "barbara-updater", "version": "3.7.4", "classifiers": [], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": [], "summary": "weather observer", "upload_time": 1732759709}, "documentation": [""], "modules": [{"name": "barbara3", "documentation": ["11/27a/24 VERSION 3.7.4 extremes, storm reports, updated labeling on baro_trace", "11/27/24 labeling baro trace at bottom and taking of y-axis labels", "11/26a/24 fixing visibility of storm reports map", "11/26/24 putting extreme button back with nws only and retries", "11/24/24 widen obs buttons for winds>100, masked extremes button while debugging, storm reports not showing", "10/28a/24 add Storm Reports Map", "10/28/24 added extremes", "10/17/24 buoys upper case, more time station plots, delete debuggin print statements. Ver 3.7.3", "10/16a/24 changing management of buoy data fetching and variable management in show_transparent_frame", "10/16/24 adjusting buoy selection to get more buoys", "10/15a/24 buoy map display fixed. Now expanding range from 500 to 2500km", "10/15/24 trying to get latest buoy map inserted during buoy help", "10/14a/24 will bring over for bobs and cobs", "10/14/24 after adding key identifier, aobs check land works", "10/13/24 incorporate buttons aobs_check_land", "10/11b/24 improve layout for buoy_help buttons", "10/11a/24 code for buoy help enter a town/state", "10/11/24 new keyboard installed", "10/10a/24 will work on layout of buoy in lat/lon for buoy help", "10/10/24 renamed buoy help functions and finding latest buoy data, filtering out 2hrs or older", "10/9b/24 including radio buttons to present choice w/ current obs working buoys near me and entered coord.", "10/9a/24 will now work to present buoy choices on a map in tkinter window", "10/9/24 when using find buoys near me, finds and prints latest obs from 3 functioning buoys to console", "10/8b/24 add button and help to get suggested buoy codes", "10/8a/24 added buoy option to site C", "10/8/24 ensure only 1 choice for lg still sat view choice", "this will be ver 3.7.2", "10/4a/24 includes other large still satellite options, and try/except block in lightning map center", "9/29a/24 chromedriver broswer sized differently on different ver. This code accommodates one version, but", "different rpis have different chromedriver versions - how to make code dynamically responsive?", "9/29/24 got isoformat error after taking out concurrence. Had to download and insert dateutil-parser", "9/27/24 Moving messages in confirm_radar_site will update 3.7.0", "ocasnl problems with unchoosing an image, reg_sat tries to build w/o a choice", "9/26/24 problems concurrency w/ obs buttons, not worth it. will replace *** maybe isoformat was the problem", "9/25b/24 4 new reg_sat views work, no zoom or full screen while working. still hangup after random, then bobs button", "9/25/24 working on obs site choice hang up, and adding reg sat choices. reg sat choice page is updated", "9/13c/24 fixed distortion on lcl radar, lightning, station plots", "9/13b/24 working on distorted selenium images - fix for 3 obs and random obs", "9/13a/24 working on dangerous clean up code", "9/13/24 added code to not allow choice of malfunctioning radar site", "9/5/24 added set position of scraped frame in national radar to prevent dead ends", "9/4a/24 working to fix error while trying to make station models. This will be 3.6.8 ", "9/4/24 working to fix connection aborted error will be ver3.6.7", "this 9/2b/24 will be renamed 9/2c/24 on all other devices and will be ver 3.6.6", "9/2b/24 changing this version (on bubba's old device) from other 9/2b/24 versions", "9/2/24 Selenium set up correctly, a and b obs sites buttons working again", "8/29/24 also programmatically install pytz and certifi this will be version 3.6.4 - not working on mine", "8/28/24 testing to successfully import folium v3.6.3", "as of 8/23/24 this is the latest version (8/21/24) that's working w/o overlapping, but concerns about folium install", "8/21A/24 change local radar queue function to avoid dead ends", "then had to install folium programmatically, correctly. ver 3.6.2", "ver 3.6.0 with maps for land sites, back buttons and stored user choices on page choose", "8/21/24 Ver 3.6.0 brief delay message when random sites chosen & improved greeting message", "8/20B/24 prevent display of back button on page choose when xs length > 0", "8/20B/24 previous choices stored from page choose for reference and reuse", "8/20A/24 now frame1 back button working for all products during initial set up", "8/20/24 finish install back buttons & other small things - not working for all products", "8/19A/24 back buttons installed up through reg sat choice", "8/19/24 add back buttons - started to mess up on page_choose"], "functions": [{"name": "barbara3.install_package", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "package_name", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Function to install a package using pip"]}, {"name": "barbara3.obs_buttons_choice_abbreviations", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "name", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "state_id", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "max_length", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "barbara3.get_disk_usage", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "path", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "barbara3.clean_apt_cache", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "barbara3.clean_up_directory", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "directory", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "free_up_threshold", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Clean up files in the given directory if free disk space is below the threshold.\n\\:param directory: Directory to clean up\n\\:param free_up_threshold: Minimum free space requi